+ * audio worker) up to NTSYNC_MAX_WAIT_COUNT+1 = 65 (cap on
+ * NtWaitForMultipleObjects).  Approach: single fixed-size cache sized to
+ * NTSYNC_Q_CACHE_MAX_ENTRIES = 16, with kmalloc fallback for total_count
+ * > 16.  16 entries comfortably covers the typical 1-8 audio wait depth;
+ * larger waits (rare) keep the existing kmalloc path with no regression.
